thms\" rel=\"noopener\">Pygorithms</a></b>\n<small>Application of mundane tasks implemented in Python. This is a compilation of simple algorithms that I wish to tackle or improve.</small></td>\n<td>\n<strong><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage/BioEye\" rel=\"noopener\">BioEye</a></strong>\n<small>College thesis &#8211; An automated facial recognition logger for video security surveillance using TensorFlow.</small></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n									web\n					<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<strong><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage/OkayHappy\" rel=\"noopener\">OkayHappy</a></strong>\n<small>A DCIT 60 Project. A simple E-commerce website solution for selling various foreign goods made for a client.</small></td>\n<td>\n<strong><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage/IntelliH\" rel=\"noopener\">IntelliH</a></strong>\n<small>Intelligent House &#8211; A UHack2017 submission. A proposed solution for protecting homes with IoT devices.</small></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<strong><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage/Cloud-Drive\" rel=\"noopener\">CloudDrive</a></strong>\n<small>A simple cloud storage solution for uploading and managing files made with barebones PHP and JavaScript.</small></td>\n<td>\n<strong><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage/newton-method\" rel=\"noopener\">newton-method</a></strong>\n<small>A simple web based Newton&#8217;s method calculator for finding the roots of any given function given by the user.</small></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n									mobile\n					<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<b><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage/dcit-26\" rel=\"noopener\">React Native Compilation</a></b>\n<small>A compilation of React Native examples for the course DCIT 26 &#8211; Application Development and Emerging Technologies.</small></td>\n<td>\n<strong><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage/Snake\" rel=\"noopener\">Snake</a></strong>\n<small>A simple snake game I developed directly on my Android phone using AIDE on my way home on the bus.</small></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n			<h2>Technology Stack</h2>		\n		<p>Technolgies that I can effectively work with.</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"https://nodejs.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/nodejs.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a></figure><p>Node.js</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"https://reactjs.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/reactjs.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a></figure><p>React.js</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"https://wordpress.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/wordpress.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a></figure><p>WordPress</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"https://laravel.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/laravel.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a></figure><p>Laravel</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"https://www.cplusplus.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/ccpp.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a></figure><p>C/C++</p>		\n			<a href=\"https://github.com/charlescabbage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n						</a>\n			<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/users/story/14446884\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n						</a>\n			<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/chrlzmndz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n						</a>', 'portfolio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-02-19 16:15:48', '2022-02-19 16:15:48', '', 17, 'http://localhost/portfolio/?p=124', 0,